widgets_values: The woman walks abit faster to catch up and walk behind the man holding onto this other arm, the camera keeps tracking with them as it gets closer to their faces
The camera goes really close on their faces as they continue to walk at a normal pace, the man looks around making sure they are not being followed as they continue walking

As they continue walking the camera arcs starts to arc around to their backs revealing the skeleton pattern on the back on the mans suit as well, there are tons of people in costumes and masks in the busy urban streets with buildings on either sides

a man wearing a skeleton mask with a black and white suit is slowly walking alongside a woman wearing a mask in a purple dress through a busy street as people cross camera, as the man starts to walk the woman moves over to the otherside of him holding his arm as they walk together
The camera continues to follow them as they head up a set of stairs
